de.uzk.hki.da.core

Class IngestAreaScannerWorker

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uzk.hki.da.core.IngestAreaScannerWorker

  • public class IngestAreaScannerWorker
extends Object
    Scans the staging area for new packages. If new files are there whose stay has been longer as specified in (minAge), they get moved to a destination area and a job gets created for them. 
    
   Staging area may look like
   .../stagingRoot/TEST1
   .../stagingRoot/TEST2
   
   and destination area like
   .../destinationRoot/TEST1
   .../destinationRoot/TEST2
    A file located under .../stagingRoot/TEST1/a.txt would then be moved to .../destinationRoot/TEST1/a.txt
    Author:
    Daniel M. de Oliveira
